The paper proposes a deep learning-based approach for travel time prediction, which is a common problem in transportation science. The paper also incorporates road network information into the model, which suggests a focus on computer vision and natural language processing techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
